experience here has been

00:49:56.667 --> 00:50:00.300
exciting and wonderful, and
I also hope that people will

00:50:00.300 --> 00:50:02.867
join me in congratulating
you in navigating

00:50:02.867 --> 00:50:05.667
which--what has been a
horrible year at Yale for

00:50:05.667 --> 00:50:07.100
all these reasons we know.

00:50:07.100 --> 00:50:09.400
And I hope that you will
leave this year armed to

00:50:09.400 --> 00:50:10.900
become a better
citizen at Yale.

00:50:10.900 --> 00:50:13.300
So
congratulations, freshmen.

00:50:13.300 --> 00:50:18.200
Professor Jonathan
Holloway: Sit down now.

00:50:18.200 --> 00:50:20.000
Seniors here?

00:50:20.000 --> 00:50:21.467
Stand up.

00:50:21.467 --> 00:50:24.200
Stand up.

