00:50:25.467 --> 00:50:27.167
This is one of your
last classes at Yale.

00:50:27.167 --> 00:50:28.167
You're going to get a lot of
people congratulating you.

00:50:28.167 --> 00:50:31.167
I'm not
congratulating you at all.

00:50:31.167 --> 00:50:35.000
A lot of people are going to
be telling you how great and

00:50:35.000 --> 00:50:36.100
wonderful you are.

00:50:36.100 --> 00:50:39.467
Oh, in the back, can you
step over one foot because

00:50:39.467 --> 00:50:42.067
you're blocking the
camera right there.

00:50:42.067 --> 00:50:43.067
There we go.

00:50:43.067 --> 00:50:44.067
