disagree with it,

00:51:08.400 --> 00:51:11.600
a history that I hope will
make you think and challenge

00:51:11.600 --> 00:51:14.000
others when they start
spouting off in the most

00:51:14.000 --> 00:51:15.700
unpredictable, or
maybe predictable,

00:51:15.700 --> 00:51:16.700
ways.

