00:51:26.400 --> 00:51:27.400
well.

00:51:27.400 --> 00:51:28.400
Congratulations.

00:51:28.400 --> 00:51:29.400
Professor Jonathan
Holloway: Sophomore,

00:51:29.400 --> 00:51:34.000
